  "short_description": "Black Trail is a VR shooter, set in an epic war in the Old West. Play as a seasoned bounty hunter and a vengeful Native American warrior, follow their interwoven stories, use a wide range of weapons, explore ravaged lands, and fight as you chase newly discovered artifacts to change the fate of war.",
