  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p>",
  "about_the_game": "It’s the gold rush era. Native people attacked the Snake Canyon mine just after a few days when white men discovered ancient artifacts. Jack, an experienced bounty hunter, and White Eagle, a respected warrior among his people, are after the same artifacts for different reasons.<br><br>Switch between characters throughout the chapters, use unique, historical weapons, fight hundreds of men in a wide Old West world, and change the fate of the war.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dive into intense and varied combat encounters with a wide range of weapons. Each weapon introduces a unique mechanic and a new play style.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/cfe9009aad7c72960536fa34ffb521a8.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/cfe9009aad7c72960536fa34ffb521a8.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/cfe9009aad7c72960536fa34ffb521a8.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Survive, defend, infiltrate, or escape! Discover a new area and overcome a new challenge in each chapter.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/74d365f720784e7ffd00cd4674a60eda.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/74d365f720784e7ffd00cd4674a60eda.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/74d365f720784e7ffd00cd4674a60eda.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Witness the clash of two worlds through the eyes of different characters and unravel the mysterious powers of ancient artifacts.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/5f4d1f525012e03c7387026878d36c94.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/5f4d1f525012e03c7387026878d36c94.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/5f4d1f525012e03c7387026878d36c94.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Unlock the Bounty Hunt after the main campaign and earn bounties when you kill in style and find timed bounty bags. Use the money to create unique weapon-enhancement combinations, and compete with other players to become a legend!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Experience a realistic and smooth VR interaction while using weapons and objects.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Choose from multiple movement and ease-of-use options designed for VR.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Follow the characters' epic stories through fully narrated and animated shorts.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Walk in delicately designed, Old West-inspired environments.</strong><br><strong>And much more!</strong><br><br><strong>Are you ready to embark on this epic adventure and prove your mettle in the wild, untamed West?</strong></li></ul>",
